divs: Sighting DetailsDid not see object in person. I was taking pictures out car window of Lake Almanor, Plumas County, CA. Speed about 60 MPH, car window was rolled down. When we got home I uploaded picture to computer and noticed object on photo. I've taken many pictures of birds from car moving at about 60 MPH. No bird ever looked like this. Shot was taken to the south looking towards the sun. Second photo attached was enlarged. Original one is just as taken from the camera. A Nikon Coolpix digital.
Summary: Object Captured in photo taken out car window. Did not see until uploaded to computer
trends: There have been no other sightings in Chester
This sighting has never been favorited.
